Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome special guest former Navy Seal and dog handler Will Chesney to discuss his raid on Osama Bin Laden and how his dog Cairo aided in tracking and killing the terrorist leader, talks about the writing of his book “No Ordinary Dog”, and describes what it is like call his parents after Bin Laden’s death.
